    "title": "Entry-Level Radiologist at Jaypee Hospital",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Jaypee Hospital. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Radiologist to strengthen our Vijayawada-based team.\n\nAbout Jaypee Hospital:\nJaypee Hospital is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Medical Ethics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Jaypee Hospital!",
